- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an unsupervised learning method for improving the performance of a classic computer vision algorithm. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in motion, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing image and video data.
